{"title":"将代码上传到github","uid":"b101d571710098ef39662d184bdacf36","slug":"github1","date":"2021-10-14T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-19T14:04:34.155Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/github1.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<p>之前一直在用hexo+Github生成静态博客，push了一次又一次，但是无非就是使用<code>hexo -cl</code>、<code>hexo -g</code>、<code>hexo -s</code>、<code>hexo -d</code>这几个命令。今天尝试将前几天写好的代码push到Github上。</p>\n<p>刚才还好好的Github，现在突然抽风打不开了，所以我用gitee演示。</p>\n<p>首先确认电脑上安装了git。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h1 id=\"第一步：初始化本地仓库\"><a href=\"#第一步：初始化本地仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第一步：初始化本地仓库\"></a>第一步：初始化本地仓库</h1><ol>\n<li><p>cd 项目文件夹</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>右键，Git Bash Here</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/github1/1.png\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>Bash里面输入<code>git init</code></p>\n<p>这时候可以看到，项目文件夹里面多了名为<code>.git</code>的隐藏文件夹。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/github1/2.png\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"第二步：远程连接\"><a href=\"#第二步：远程连接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第二步：远程连接\"></a>第二步：远程连接</h1><ol>\n<li><p>创建并初始化仓库，复制仓库地址。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/github1/3.png\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>git remote add origin https://仓库地址</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>通过<code>git remote -v</code>命令查看</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/github1/4.png\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>hint:我之前已经添加过仓库了所以第一个命令提示error</p></blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"第三步：推送到远程仓库\"><a href=\"#第三步：推送到远程仓库\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"第三步：推送到远程仓库\"></a>第三步：推送到远程仓库</h1><ol>\n<li><p><code>git add .</code>将文件夹下的所有文件添加到暂存区。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>git commit -m &quot;备注&quot;</code>提交暂存区的文件到本地仓库。</p>\n<p>这里的备注将会在仓库那里显示出来（文件名后面）。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/github1/7.png\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>git pull --rebase origin master</code>将本地仓库和远程仓库同步</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>这时候会发现工作目录下多了两个README.md文件。</p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><p><code>git push -u origin master</code>将缓冲区的文件推送到远程仓库。</p>\n<p> <img src=\"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/github1/6.png\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"注意\"><a href=\"#注意\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意\"></a>注意</h1><p>origin的名称要统一</p>\n<p>如果你习惯使用origion那么就一直用origion，否则就一直用origin。两个混用会报错。</p>\n","text":"之前一直在用hexo+Github生成静态博客，push了一次又一次，但是无非就是使用hexo -cl、hexo -g、hexo -s、hexo -d这几个命令。今天尝试将前几天写好的代码push到Github上。 刚才还好好的Github，现在突然抽风打不开了，所以我用gite...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":676,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"分享","slug":"分享","count":11,"path":"api/categories/分享.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"git","slug":"git","count":1,"path":"api/tags/git.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第一步：初始化本地仓库</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第二步：远程连接</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%8E%A8%E9%80%81%E5%88%B0%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E4%BB%93%E5%BA%93\"><span class=\"toc-text\">第三步：推送到远程仓库</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">注意</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"砂糖","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cloud.fullcomb.top/private/source/image/build/Ryza/avatar.png","link":"/","description":"盐港鸣笛声  催扬帆出海<br>方觉时光匆匆已过三载<audio controls><source src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1366594775.mp3\"></audio>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Satoing","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"iconfont icon-bilibili-fill","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/52750318"},"Leetcode":{"icon":"iconfont icon-leetcode","link":"https://leetcode.cn/u/satoing/"}}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"线性表的应用1：就地逆置","uid":"6ca5cfdcc88d992061c4e3a61cb4678b","slug":"reverse","date":"2021-10-15T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-19T14:04:19.388Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articl